{"tid":1280002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於個別自殺既報導守則","createTime":"2019-07-02T23:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T23:14:53.000Z","uid":233835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4a12b705053fe0de38a6f1ab72bb75bb6ad105bb","tid":1280002,"uid":233835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:14:53.000Z","msg":"早前有人話，點解咁多個media都唔報導IFC果單野<br />\n<br />\n希望大家會明白，令身邊既人知道。<br />\n<br />\n其實係有個守則 / 指引係入面<br />\n<br />\n- 不宜完全不報道個別的自殺案件 , 而應在報道自殺新聞和避免產生「模仿」效應之間求取平衡。<br />\n<br />\n- 煽情的報道手法會引致模仿效應；<br />\n<br />\n- 不要將自殺光榮化或聳動化。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkja.org.hk/%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87%E5%8F%8A%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95/%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E5%B0%8D%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkja.org.hk%2F%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2589%2587%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BC%2595%2F%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BC%2595%2F&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=db20c212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkja.org.hk/%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87%E5%8F%8A%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95/%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E5%B0%8D%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AD%E8%A6%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%258E%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AD%25E8%25A6%2581&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=b8a799ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AD%E8%A6%81<